{"tid":1785550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偽黃絲得把口 鄙視","createTime":"2019-12-16T12:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T17:26:35.000Z","uid":340975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3178c2261d71d5dbad83ff7bef3ef34074b7433a","tid":1785550,"uid":340975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"屋企次次都得我單拖出。<br />\n佢地都會鬧popo，但成日扮哂識野叫我出街唔好亂講野，叫佢地去遊行就多多藉口，有時真係好嬲，想鬧佢地一餐，把口知道香港而家嘅處境，但咩都冇做過，仲可以笑笑口去講呢排啲新聞。<br />\n我唔想係一個偽黃絲家庭入面，得把口。<br />\n一面鬧完警謊，一面竟然可以好開心咁話返大陸過年。我好懷疑到底兩老有冇當過自己係香港人，更諗唔明同我一樣土生土長嘅brother點解會好似局外人咁，我未做到去勇武，但至少做個勉強合格嘅和理非。<br />\n真係好sad。<br />\n手足，街上見。"},{"pid":"fe8bd35cacbbaf31da36a0be93f1c8347b9d0560","tid":1785550,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7febf6744f3043e47db6b34059b537cfcea1728c","tid":1785550,"uid":310982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c97314ac1e93e9879f891046b2827b4aa52bcd6c","tid":1785550,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a3180174855dd7d7ddc18afaf5c9e10809f015d","tid":1785550,"uid":47542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"身邊好多偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時都分唔到係咪同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa08a853dedb850e3be6ffe8912892061d03476","tid":1785550,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"咁你係咪情願佢地係藍呀？"},{"pid":"893b914b9bff37ad336db7bf71d956e9e92af134","tid":1785550,"uid":340975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa08a853dedb850e3be6ffe8912892061d03476","tid":1785550,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"咁你係咪情願佢地係藍呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"藍係腦閉塞 偽黃係虛偽<br />\n冇比較好都係衰<br />\n如果係藍 直接割"},{"pid":"0cb3128ba7c03c321e04242c930d94eb6fe37951","tid":1785550,"uid":340975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a3180174855dd7d7ddc18afaf5c9e10809f015d","tid":1785550,"uid":47542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"身邊好多偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時都分唔到係咪同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}